  %BETWEEN%
  mu BY y1-y20@1;
  mu;
  [mu];
  [y1-y20@0];
  y1-y20@0;

  day_ar by day_ar1-day_ar19@1;

  [resvar];
  resvar2-resvar20@0;
  [resvar2-resvar20@0];

  mu night_ar day_ar resvar_1 resvar WITH
    mu night_ar day_ar resvar_1 resvar;

  OUTPUT:

  PLOT:

  FACTOR = ALL (500);
